sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as rhods-dashboard<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModReg as model-registry-ui<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS
    participant GenAI as gen-ai-ui<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS
    participant Perses as data-science-perses<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Accesses Dashboard (Gateway API Pattern)
    User->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (serving cert)
    KRBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS<br/>SA token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBAC: Auth Decision
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080 (localhost)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User<br/>X-Auth-Request-Groups
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 TLS<br/>User-impersonated token
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: Resource Response
    Dashboard-->>KRBAC: HTML/JSON Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over Dashboard,GenAI: Flow 2: Module Federation (Micro-Frontend Loading)
    User->>Gateway: Request /model-registry/*
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080
    Dashboard->>ModReg: HTTPS/8043 TLS<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    ModReg-->>Dashboard: Module Assets/API Response
    Dashboard-->>User: Federated Response

    User->>Gateway: Request /gen-ai/*
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080
    Dashboard->>GenAI: HTTPS/8143 TLS<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    GenAI-->>Dashboard: Module Assets/API Response
    Dashboard-->>User: Federated Response

    Note over Dashboard,Perses: Flow 4: Observability Proxy
    Dashboard->>Perses: HTTP/8080<br/>User token
    Perses-->>Dashboard: Metrics Data
